User refreshing / No polling

Go to tests tab:
  -> Make a call to /reports/info -> [a, b, c] -> /summary, /test_cases, /test_suites
  -> Make a call to /tests/info -> [b, d, e] -> /overview

  b -> TI + reports
  a, c -> reports
  d, e -> TI

If both are empty
  -> Don't show anything.

If any of them are non-empty:
  -> dropdown with union of [a,b,c] and [b,d,e]
  -> show info wrt their position
